Package com.phasmidsoftware.dsaipg.graphs.tunnels

Class TunnelProperties

java.lang.Object
com.phasmidsoftware.dsaipg.graphs.tunnels.TunnelProperties
All Implemented Interfaces:
Sequenced, Comparable<TunnelProperties>
public class TunnelProperties extends Object implements Sequenced, Comparable<TunnelProperties>
The TunnelProperties class represents the properties of a tunnel, including cost, length, phase, and sequence. It implements the Sequenced interface for maintaining sequence information and provides comparison functionality to facilitate ordering based on cost.

  • Constructor Details

    • TunnelProperties

      public TunnelProperties(long cost, int length, int phase, int sequence)
      Constructs a TunnelProperties object with the specified cost, length, phase, and sequence.
      Parameters:
      cost - the cost associated with the tunnel, represented as a long value
      length - the length of the tunnel in meters, represented as an integer
      phase - the phase of the tunnel, where 0 indicates an "existing" tunnel and 1 indicates a "new" tunnel
      sequence - the sequence number associated with the tunnel, represented as an integer
